Feb 12, 2019  V.1.0.0. release
+------------------------------------+
- Fixed issue close of some dialogs
- Added some dialog boxes before accidental closure with unsaved data
- improved the informations on dialogs and frames
- Add new menu items
- The Todays lesson has a button to enable a new lesson 
- Fixed system base paths when install via pip with the '--user' flag 
  (on linux and MacOs)
